summary: Completed comprehensive frontend testing of Mission Control UI. All major features working correctly and matching design requirements.
passed_tests: Header displays MISSION CONTROL logo correctly
Agent count (6) and task count (0) displayed correctly
Time display and ONLINE status with green indicator working
Navigation buttons (Active, Chat, Broadcast, Docs) all clickable and functional
Left sidebar AGENTS section with count display working
All Agents card with progress ring displaying correctly
Individual agent cards show emoji avatars, names, level tags (LEAD/SPC/INT), WORKING status, and roles
Mission Queue header with filter tabs (All, Inbox, Assigned, Active, Review, Done, Waiting) all functional
Three column Kanban layout (ASSIGNED, IN PROGRESS, REVIEW) displaying correctly
Agent filtering functionality working when clicking individual agents
View mode switching between Active, Chat, Broadcast, and Docs working properly
